com.google.gwt.user.client.EventListener, SearchCriteriaItemListener
public class SearchCriteriaSummary
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Composite
implements SearchCriteriaItemListener

The graphical element that makes a visual summary of the selected filter/criteria for the search. This widget controls the unselected of a filter/criteria, and implements methods for managing the summary of SearchCriteriaTriplets

Author:
jgutierrez
